20
00:01:03,392 --> 00:01:09,952
=The Empress Dowager On A Second Spring=

21
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:14,959
Release the Empress Dowager,

22
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,920
and I'll proclaim
the prince as Crown Prince.

23
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,359
You'll be in charge of court affairs.

24
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,280
I'll feign illness and retire.

25
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:24,519
I'll nurture the prince for you.

26
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:28,159
Your son will inherit
the legitimate throne.

27
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,680
This way,

28
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,799
your descendants gain the empire,

29
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:34,400
and you'll be remembered
in history as a virtuous prince,

30
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,760
leaving an illustrious name.

31
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,799
Two birds with one stone.

32
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,159
How unexpected.

33
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,920
