for the Empress Dowager?

34
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,400
One more condition.

35
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,239
I'll take the prince back.

36
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,760
Don't even think about it.

37
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,519
The Crown Prince shouldn't stay outside.

38
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,359
Uncle, don't forget.

39
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,519
