49
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:16,224
The Empress Dowager

50
00:02:16,928 --> 00:02:17,664
and the prince...

51
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,560
I'll take them back with me.

52
00:02:34,528 --> 00:02:36,256
Your demise approaches.

53
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:43,960
