73
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,519
Today's the Empress Dowager
and my uncle's wedding.

74
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,680
Shouldn't you be defending our borders?

75
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,160
Why come unsummoned?

76
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,399
I fight desperately at the frontier,

77
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:37,279
but you scorn my daughter,

78
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:40,000
denying her the empress title!

79
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:43,240
Abdicate to the Regent now.

80
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,240
Your Grace.

81
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:48,360
Did I arrive in time?

82
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,319
I planned to let He An relinquish

83
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:55,199
the throne after the wedding ceremony.

84
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,680
Minor complications arose,

85
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,439
but they matter not.

86
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,120
He An.

87
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:04,240
The palace is now surrounded
by elite troops.

88
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,879
Resistance is futile.

89
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,759
Abdicate to me,

90
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:12,879
