97
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,079
Someone.

98
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,600
Secure the Empress Dowager.

99
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:38,720
Who dares?

100
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,720
