106
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,439
You reject courtesy for coercion?

107
00:06:57,959 --> 00:07:00,240
Abdicate or face deposition.

108
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,600
While I live,

109
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,560
