His Majesty or Her Majesty!

110
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,519
Yu Feng.

111
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,079
I acknowledge your heroism

112
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,040
and loyalty.

113
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,560
Lay down your arms

114
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,480
and surrender to me,

115
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,079
and I'll appoint you as Grand General.

116
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,920
Never!

117
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,199
Well then,

118
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,279
I'll show no mercy.

119
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,879
General Ding.

120
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:19,639
Yes.

121
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:21,639
Arrest everyone in this hall.

122
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,160
Those who surrender

123
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,800
shall be promoted.

124
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,176
The resistant ones

125
00:07:26,784 --> 00:07:27,879
shall be executed now!

126
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,800
Your Majesty, ascend the throne.

127
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,560
- Ascend the throne.
- Ascend the throne.

128
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:35,639
Your Majesty,

129
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,439
won't you join me?

130
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,319
No, this...

131
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,800
General.

132
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,839
What are you doing?

133
00:07:58,839 --> 00:07:59,759
What am I doing?

134
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:01,720
If you kill my future son-in-law,

135
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:04,319
my precious daughter
would become a widow.

136
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:06,624
Moreover, your personal guards
and assassins

137
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,740
have all been killed.

138
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:08,940
We also found evidence

139
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:10,920
