and collusion in your manor.

140
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,040
How dare you betray me?

141
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,639
My daughter is about
to become the Empress.

142
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:20,288
Why would the father
of the future Empress rebel?

143
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,240
Seize him!

144
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:28,240
Please forgive me.

145
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,800
I feared information leakage,

146
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,759
which led to this staged performance.

147
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,039
I offended Your Majesty.

148
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,559
Rise, General.

149
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,919
Thank you, Your Majesty.

150
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,279
So

151
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,480
you didn't collude with the Regent?

152
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:40,879
Well...

153
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,000
Not exactly.

154
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,639
Perhaps we should invite him

155
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,519
to explain everything to Your Majesty.

156
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,720
Master.

157
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,600
My rescue comes too late.

158
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,879
Please forgive me.

159
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,039
You're alive!

160
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:15,080
Regarding this matter,

161
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:17,200
it all began at the one-year-old catch,

162
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:18,879
with Ziru's arrest

163
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:20,360
and release.

164
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,200
A letter from the frontier?

165
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,559
Marquis Jingyuan.

166
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:29,759
Marquis Jingyuan?

167
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,360
How are you connected to him?

168
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,360
He served under my late father,

169
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,320
who once headed the Ministry of War

170
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:38,039
and was the late Empress's father.

171
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,639
Your father
was the previous Empress's father?

172
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,879
Then you must be...

173
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:43,199
The late Empress

174
00:09:43,456 --> 00:09:44,256
was my sister.

175
00:09:44,352 --> 00:09:47,480
But your surname...

176
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,600
I was adopted and changed my surname.

177
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:51,080
I kept it quiet

178
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:53,559
to better protect
my sister and His Majesty.

179
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,399
Before she passed, she made me

180
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,639
promise to protect His Majesty

181
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,080
and told me to turn

182
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,320
to Marquis Jingyuan if needed.

183
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:04,600
So Marquis Jingyuan's dealings
with the Regent

184
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:07,279
were actually to protect His Majesty.

185
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,559
No wonder

186
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:10,240
you trust Ding Yi completely.

187
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,320
So your plan

188
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:14,360
involved Marquis Jingyuan
from the start.

189
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:16,120
Correct.

190
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,799
If the Regent takes the bait,

191
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:19,480
he'll transfer me to the frontier

192
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,679
and order Marquis Jingyuan

193
00:10:22,399 --> 00:10:23,720
to kill me at the border.

194
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,159
Good.

195
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,679
Brilliant plot.

196
