200
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,679
The soldiers' words

201
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,159
were staged by the Marquis

202
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,440
and me.

203
00:10:38,879 --> 00:10:40,279
The fire was staged.

204
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,519
The burned remains

205
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:43,200
were a straw effigy.

206
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,440
To convince him

207
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,679
of Ziru's death,

208
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,919
I had to perform

209
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:51,360
