226
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,399
No time to waste.

227
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,720
Let's hurry to the capital.

228
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,120
Since he wants a grand wedding,

229
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,279
