240
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,240
We even have a child.

241
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,600
He's the Crown Prince!

242
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,519
The Crown Prince.

243
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,159
I forgot to tell you.

244
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,232
The blood paternity test was fake.

245
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,429
Xiao Hu

246
00:12:17,184 --> 00:12:20,120
