247
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,360
I don't believe it.

248
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,440
I don't believe!

249
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,240
Let her go!

250
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:28,600
Nobody move!

251
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,159
If anyone approaches,

252
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,840
I'll take her life with mine!

